des: How much do you know about wine? Whether you choose grapes by the label or the year, this quiz is fun for all levels. In Oregon, winemakers are farmers and they get stoked when talking about the art and science of wine making. Open this Alexa skill for a quick brain teaser or an escape to lovely Oregon wine country. Pick the correct answer that leads you to exclusive stories. Challenge your friends and family to take and retake the quiz. Just no cheating. Ask Alexa to 'open Oregon Wine Quiz.'
